description: Metadata about Table row change set.

tableId.description: The ID of the table that this change is for.

rowVersion.description: The version number of the table row change

headers.description: The list of ColumnModels ID that describes the rows of this change.

createdOn.description: The date this change was created.

createdBy.description: The ID of the user that created this change.

bucket.description: The name of the S3 bucket where this change is stored

key.description: The name of the S3 key where this change is stored
